data.description: Home is back on the market & vacant!! Gorgeous resale home in Dekalb County!! This well-maintained property boasts numerous desirable features that make it a great opportunity for potential buyers. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths, this home offers great living space for families of all sizes. The large flat leveled backyard is the perfect space for outdoor activities, gardening, or even the addition of a pool or patio. Location is everything, and this property does not disappoint. Situated in Dekalb County, it offers the convenience of being close to the Gwinnett line, granting easy access to both counties. Whether it's for work, shopping, or entertainment, this prime location ensures that everything you need is just a short drive away. As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by its attractive full brick front and the convenience of a 2-car garage, providing ample parking space. Beautiful sunken family room, with a cozy fireplace, that creates a very inviting atmosphere, connected to the open kitchen, making it a perfect space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family & friends. The master bedroom is a true oasis, offering an abundance of space and a separate sitting area for relaxation or a private retreat. The large master bathroom is an added bonus, providing a luxurious experience for the homeowner. Although the home needs new carpet, it is in good condition overall, thanks to the diligent care taken by the owners. With a little personal touch and customization, this property has the potential to become your dream home. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a well-maintained home in a highly sought-after location. Schedule a viewing today and make this house your own, enjoying all the comforts and conveniences it has to offer!
